Day 13: Empower, Don’t Dictate!
💪 "Scrum Masters don’t push—they empower teams to pull!"  
👉 Tip: Let your team own their decisions and process. Your role is to guide, not command.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How often do you empower your team to make their own decisions?"  
1. Always 💪  
2. Most of the time 🤝  
3. Sometimes 🧑‍🤝‍🧑  
4. Rarely 🚦
